Feature: Attendee Wants
  In order to have a nicer code camp server
  As a code camp attendee
  I want to be able to do some fun things

  Scenario: I want to be able to follow the code camp on Twitter

  Scenario: I want to be able to add a badge to my website to let people know I am attending this event

  Scenario: I want to be able to subscribe to email updates about the event

  Scenario: I want the website to look nice in my mobile browser
